<FTL>

<!-- Basically an extra vampiric weapon with various events and RadiKal-style spice. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM">
    <title>Shipvore Ram</title>
    <desc>The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, Full Power uses more and destroys the augment. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]
	
	Can be reinforced at empty beacons to survive the next Full Power use.
	</desc>
    <cost>70</cost>
	<!--<bp>4</bp>-->
    <rarity>3</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM">
    <title>Shipvore Ram</title>
    <desc>The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, Full Power uses more. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]
	
	The ship was built around this locked version that survives Full Power use. Also gives 9% faster shield recharge and chance to ignore hull damage.
	</desc>
    <cost>200</cost>
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>


<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF">
    <title>Charged Belts (Off)</title>
    <desc>(RK Bam gear) This augment is Off but can be toggled On anytime. When On: 
	[This double-edged augment equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Vagabonds) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.
	Stacks upon already existing death effects.
	
	Cannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.

	COMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.]</desc>
    <cost>50</cost>		
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON">
    <title>Charged Belts</title>
    <desc>(RK Bam gear) This double-edged augment equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Vagabonds) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.
	Stacks upon already existing death effects.
	
	Cannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.

	COMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.</desc>
    <cost>50</cost>		
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Can trigger immediately if below HP threshold when choosing to activate it in combat check. -->
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_AUG_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR">
    <title>A.E.R.A. Second Wind</title>
    <desc>(RK Bam gear) 'Automated Emergency Repair Augment'. 
		When active, if your ship is almost destroyed (5 hull or less), a nanomachine burst will be released in your systems, fully repairing them as well as 8 hull points, and destroying the augment. No effect if your hull instantly reaches 0. [Activation uses 1 power, Emergency Generator can apply]</desc>
    <cost>60</cost>
    <rarity>3</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_LEAD_TITANS">
    <title>Lead Titans</title>
    <desc>(RK Bam gear) Someone had the insane idea to weave motile fiber-lead into muscles. 
		
		Your 'big' crew (Crystals, Rockmen, and Lanius) have: 2.5x resistance to everything, 3.5x damage to everything.
		The weight makes them take 2 crew slots, create breaches while walking, and they can't repair.
		Your other crew get a flat +75% repair speed from smaller fibers.

		All your crew gain a flat +50% movement speed.</desc>
    <cost>70</cost>
    <rarity>4</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="RK_BAM_DIVINE_ARMOR">
    <title>Thicker Hull</title>
    <desc>(RK Bam gear) RadiKals reverse engineered extremely rare armor into this slightly more accessible armor, but it reduces weapon charge speed by 5%.
		Impacts that deal 1 damage have a 40% chance to be negated, and all other damage is reduced by 1.
	</desc>
    <cost>130</cost>
    <rarity>0</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
	<value>0.4</value>			<!-- THIS IS THE CHANCE TO NEGATE 1-DAMAGE HITS via the Lua!!! -->
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="RK_PERSISTENCE_SHIELD">
    <title>Persistence Shield</title>
	<desc>(RK Bam gear) Adds a 4 hitpoints Super Shield. Stacks with other super shields, but not with itself.
		Also increases shield charge speed by 20%.
		
		Activate from the Toggle Menu to instantly restore all your Supershield layers. [Uses 1 {]
		Cannot be activated again until you rebuild its capacitor at an empty beacon for 7~ .
	</desc>
    <cost>130</cost>
    <rarity>5</rarity>
    <stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
</FTL>

