<FTL>

<!-- TEST: DEBUGS NONSENSICAL "Scorched Earth" tiers TEST RESULTS? (T1 protecting a little, T2&T3 doing nothing)
=> This aug itself works perfectly fine. Evens stacks with T1 Scorched Earth for "negative" fire damage
(that cannot repair damaged bars above it though) -->
<augBlueprint name="FIRE_IMMUNITY">
	<!-- <title id="fusion_aug_FIRE_IMMUNITY_title"/>Fire Immunity
	<desc id="fusion_aug_FIRE_IMMUNITY_desc"/>Systems don't take fire damage. -->
	<title>Fire Immunity</title>
	<desc>Systems take 100% less fire damage.</desc>
	<cost>45</cost>
	<bp>4</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<value>1</value>
	<stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Each level increases the fire resists.
The first one allows widespread own ship fire control (removal and creation) and survival, with heal. -->
<augBlueprint name="RK_SCORCH_SELF">
    <title>Scorched Earth (T1)</title>
    <desc>(RK Scorch gear) Your crew take 0.6x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.
	
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.
	
	Can be upgraded twice at empty beacons, increasing the fire resistances and gaining an effect.</desc>
    <cost>60</cost>
    <rarity>3</rarity>
	<!-- <value>1</value> This field is unneeded and can't fix system fire resistance. -->
    <!-- <stackable>false</stackable> -->
    <stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Better res, potential infinity loop. -->
<augBlueprint name="RK_SCORCH_SELF_2">
    <title>Blazing Earth (T2)</title>
    <desc>(RK Scorch gear) [Tier 2 Scorched Earth] Your crew take 0.45x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.
		In fire, they also produce O2 like 1 Orchid.
	
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.
	
	Can be upgraded once at empty beacons, increasing the fire resistances and O2 production.</desc>
    <cost>90</cost>			
    <rarity>5</rarity>
	<!-- <value>1</value> This field is unneeded and can't fix system fire resistance. -->
    <!-- <stackable>false</stackable> -->
    <stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<!-- Better res, facilitate infinity loop. -->
<augBlueprint name="RK_SCORCH_SELF_3">
    <!-- <title>Molten Earth</title> -->
	<title>Erupting Earth (T3)</title>
    <desc>(RK Scorch gear) [Tier 3 Scorched Earth] Your crew take 0.3x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.
		In fire, they also produce O2 like 3 Orchids.
	
	Activate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.
	
	COMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.</desc>
    <cost>120</cost>
    <rarity>0</rarity>
	<!-- <value>1</value> This field is unneeded and can't fix system fire resistance. -->
    <!-- <stackable>false</stackable> -->
    <stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>


<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_ENEMY">
	<title>Plasma Teleporter</title>
	<desc>(RK Scorch gear) This combat augment can set the enemy ship on fire at start of combat, outright winning some fights.
		Needs a fire source: RK firestarting equipment, Gouls, Lost Suns, Shells, Zoltans, or 3}.
		[Uses 1{, ignites your O2 system.]

	COMBO: Charged Belts / Martyr Vests make all crew fire sources.
	COMBO: any Scorched Earth can provide the fire for free.</desc>
	<cost>75</cost>
	<rarity>5</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_ENEMIES_CAN_BURN">
	<title>Flammabilizer-Immune</title>
	<desc>(RK Scorch gear) Passively removes the fire immunity of enemies, and limits their fire resistance to 0%. Enemies who invert fire damage stop doing that. Vulnerable enemies (like Orchids) are unaffected.
	Works on both ships.

	Can be toggled anytime to make non-fireproof enemies take more fire damage instead.
	Both toggle modes make enemies move 20% slower in fire (up to 80% with 3 power in O2).</desc>
	<cost>100</cost>
	<rarity>5</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_ENEMIES_BURN_MORE">
	<title>Flammabilizer-Damage</title>
	<desc>(RK Scorch gear) Passively makes enemies who can burn take 75% more fire damage, scaling up to 375% with 4 power in your Life Support (O2) system.
	Works on both ships.
	
	Can be toggled anytime to make fireproof and fire-resistant enemies vulnerable to fire instead.
	Both toggle modes make enemies move 20% slower in fire (up to 80% with 3 power in O2).</desc>
	<cost>100</cost>
	<rarity>5</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="DJMOD_OXYGENIZER">
	<title>Oxygenizer</title>
	<desc>This RadiKal Scorch combat augment can basically shoot out giant canisters of ultracompressed O2 to fill the void of space when a fight starts.
	Puts both ships in an atmosphere, making breaches and open vents fill oxygen instead of depleting it. Shenanigans ensue. [Uses 2}]</desc>
	<cost>20</cost>
	<rarity>4</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
</FTL>

