<FTL>

 <!-- <descriptionOverride>TEXT</descriptionOverride>
Overrides the weapon's description you see when you open your inventory menu, with whatever you'd like it to say. The reason you would want this is if you say, wanted to hide the fact that the weapon spawned crew, such as my example below.
Example
 <descriptionOverride>Fires a photonic blast that can disrupt shields like normal lasers, but only deals system damage with a low chance to start a fire or breach. A ship would have to be close to destruction for this to possibly destroy it.
    
Stats:   
Required Power: 1
Charge Time: 8 seconds

Shot Radius: 35
Shots Per Charge: 3

Total System Damage: 1

Fire Chance: 10%


Buy/Sell Price: 120~/60~
</descriptionOverride> -->

