	<flavorType>Ion Blast</flavorType>
	<title>Rain of Ions</title>
	<short>Rain Ions</short>
	<tip>tip_phase</tip>
	<locked>1</locked>			<!-- what's that? -->
	<desc>(RK Punk gear) This heavy duty shotgun fires an accelerated phase ion, a heavy ion, a fire ion, a normal ion, a stun ion, and a radion (from fastest to slowest) all at once. Chains cooldown up to 4 times.
		Many weapons worth of blue options!
	</desc>
	<!-- <tooltip>Fires all 6 common ions in a radius; Cooldown 12 seconds.</tooltip>	Tooltips don't show with a <tip> set -->
