<!-- Missile weapon staggered just right so that the 100% chance fire they create never ends.
Pre-rework: burns 2 bars (3 on 6tiles rooms like obelisk weapon room) through extinguishers,
with a long cooldown so you cant just spray an O2 ship. Small targeting radius to allow for rare collateral fires on O2 ships when targeting smaller than 2x2 tile rooms.

v5.5.1 rework: chains to lower cooldown so you CAN spray fire then. 
DO NOT remove the EnemyFix version, they shoot multiple rooms with each cooldown so it's very different for them. -->
